<HEADLINE> Skier, Snowboarder Die in Collision </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	BRECKENRIDGE, Colo. (AP) -- A teenage skier launched off a jump  
here Saturday and crashed into a 59-year-old snowboarder, killing 
both. 
</P>
